{
  "stem": "8352.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So that's why we were all the families pushed in-- little children, infants, and all kinds of things-- in those wagons.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we arrived to Mateszalka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They let us out of there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They pushed us out in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there were some kind of barracks-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some little buildings.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "It's like tents out of canvas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And there where we had to stay and-- and wait, see what happened next.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they were also with-- all the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brothers were-- we didn't know about the brothers after.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was only with my two sisters, me and my father, and my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brothers were in the army somewhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't know after we left the-- the town where they were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or they didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know about each other at all in that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, one of my brothers we didn't know, because the Hungarian were sending the Jewish soldiers to dig mines out in the front somewhere.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those mines exploded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a lot of the Jewish soldiers were getting killed or just destroyed, you know, blowing up the bodies.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had a letter from the Hungarian army that one of the brother-- one of our brothers is disappeared.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know where he is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was rumors that a lot of the guys were running.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were hiding out and giving themselves up to the partisans, to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we always thought in our mind that he is alive somewhere-- maybe he run away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And someday, we will meet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we never heard about him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the only time that we had a-- a statement from the Hungarian government that he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
